{"tid":429978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ICC首席檢察官 涉收賄洩敏感資料","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T12:40:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"328967548effa608d1f19129c22982a3213e02ce","tid":429978,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176697&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176697%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&d=hAoLjnH3VPVtREvRwMsKRIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=60200dbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176697%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&h=41e501b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176697&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009</a><br />\n<br />\nICC首席檢察官<br />\n涉收賄洩敏感資料<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\nICC前首席檢察官奧坎波<br />\n<br />\n奧坎波擔任ICC首席檢察官9年，上周有報道指他涉嫌收取賄賂，向懷疑犯下戰爭罪行的人提供敏感資料，據報ICC已就此事調查兩名員工。今次外洩的電郵，顯示他喜歡巴結權貴名人，想借他們的影響力幫忙查案。<br />\n<br />\n向佐治古尼借衞星<br />\n<br />\n電郵顯示，除了安琪蓮娜祖莉，奧坎波又曾經聯絡影星佐治古尼求助，後者曾發起一項計劃，利用商用人造衞星監察南蘇丹的戰爭罪行證據。奧坎波想借用這衞星網，調查利比亞前獨裁者卡達菲在2011年內戰期間的暴行，只是佐治古尼以衞星未夠精密為由婉拒。奧坎波又曾邀請金像影帝辛潘一同出席聯合國安理會有關蘇丹的會議，還表示正考慮是否就巴勒斯坦地區的衝突啟動調查，最終對方確受此事吸引，與他在紐約見面。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t傳安琪蓮娜願施美人計誘捕烏干達軍閥<br />\n國際要聞 14小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/small/09wk9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Fsmall%2F09wk9p.jpg&h=0bf1a0b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06a1ef76f0b764432a05153e273830a645785324","tid":429978,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6398d7072d25f0c8a79fc952f4aaa764519b754","tid":429978,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>看錯ICAC</blockquote><br />\nX2"}]}